  "texts": [
    "While Mixtral-based models perform on par, the 7b parameter models fall short compared to their English counterparts.",
    "This is especially true for DiscoLM.",
    "Although it is one of the best German models, it performs exceptionally well in English tests, outperforming all 13B models tested.",
    "The bilingual LeoLM got an even higher score from Auto-J than DiscoLM for English answers, but produced mainly unusable answers in German language.",
    "It is also a notable exception for the congruence of scores from JudgeLM and Auto-J."
